title: Prison Architect Mod: Star Wars - Imperial Architect (8/4/2014)
description:
This is for a Star Wars themed mod for the indie game Prison Architect

The Official Steam Workshop page for the game is here:

All credit goes to the original creator, Vector, i'm just sharing

Steam Workshop description:

*** Works with Alpha 23 *** 

Imperial Architect is a fan made Star Wars conversion mod of the original Prison Architect Game. 

Currently the Imperial Architect mod like the original Prison Architect game is still under development and therefore will be receiving regular updates in order to keep the mod up to date with the current version of Prison Architect. 

Please post any bugs or suggestions you have within the Forum section. 

Thanks. 

- Vector.
